vaikuMTha varNane
tatvasAra - vaikuMTha varNane
|| muktisaMdhi ||
tatvasArada sobaga dhareyoLu |
vistarisabEkeMdu munikula ratna shrIguruvAdirAjanu shrutipurANagaLa
mottavanu nere mathisi mElaNa |
mukti sRuShTisthitilayaMgaLa arthiyiMdali baNNisida kathe kELi sajjanaru ||
idu puNyakathe lOkakkide mukutiya patha ida kELuvavane kRutArtha |
idu sarvasAdhana vidhugaLige sammata mudavanIvudu kELvajanake || 1 ||
mElenipa nATi modalAda rAgaMgaLa tALamELadi nAlkusaMdhi |
shrIlOlana carite tatvarahasyada mAle kELvarigalaMkAra || 2 ||
kannaDiyoLippaMtha pUrNaprajnara mata dunnata tatvasAravanu |
kannaDadi baNNisida vAdirAjamuniya binnapavanellaru mannipudu || 3 ||
shlOka - shlukAMbaradharaM viShNuM shashivarNaM caturBujaM |
prasannavadanaM dhyAyEtsarva viGnOpashAMtayE ||
pada : niShkaLaMka caMdravadana shuklavasana lakSha shashivarNa prasanna |
nAlkutOLina viShNu namma viGnaMgaLa gakkane oresi rakShisabEku || 4 ||
shlOka - nArAyaNaM namaskRutya naraM caiva narOttamaM |
dEvIM sarasvatIM vyAsaM tatOjayamudIrayEt ||
pada : naraneMdu shEShana pesaru nArAyaNana mereva mUlarUpavenipa |
guruvyAsa narOttama vAyu dEvilakumi sarasvati graMthadoDati gaDa || 5 ||
graMthamADida vEdavyAsa munIMdranna vRuMdAraka guruveMdoMdisitu |
iMdirEshaneMba mUlanArAyaNana ceMduLLa pesareMdoMdisitu || 6 ||
vANiya balagoMbe prANanAthana pAdakkAneraguve rameyaDige |
A namisuve hayavadana dEvOttamana mAnasadalliTTu neneve || 7 ||

shlOka - lakShmInArAyaNaM vaMdE tadBakta pravarO hi yaH |
shrImadAnaMdatIrthAKyO gurustaMca namAmyahaM ||
EtAvatAlaM nanu sUcitEna guNairasAmyE&nati shAyanO&sya
hitvEtarAn prArthayatO viBUtiH yasyAMGrirENuM juShatEna&BIpsOH ||
mikkadEvarkaLa lekkisade lakumi mana ukki Atage mAleyikkidaLu
akkareyiMdali lakuminarEyaNargeragi tadBakta madhvamunige sharaNeMbe || 8 ||
shlOka - tRutIyamasya vRuShaBasya dOhasE dashapramatiM janayaMta
yOShaNaH |
yadI manu pradivO madhva AdhavE mahAsaMtaM mAtarishvA mathAyati ||
siriBUmi durgeyaru jnAnAmRutava karevare guru pUrNaprajnara puTTisidaru
gaDa |
naralOkada nArige ivara heruva BAgya dorakadeMdu shruti yOShaNayeMditu || 9 ||
dashamatiyeMba pesaremma guruvaranige dashadishagaLalli prasiddha kANiro |
eseva I nAmavanimiSharoLobbarigilla
RuShigilla mAnisaroLilla nAmaPala baladiMdemma guruvigidu dharma || 10 ||
pUrNaprajnareMba nAma namma guruvaraguMTu unnatOpaniShattu sarvaveMba
shabdakke
pUrNaveMbarthava pELitAgi dashamatiyeMbudana pELuvude madhvamunigallade
innu uttarOttaranollade pUrvOktipELvude || 11 ||
idu dEvaroLu vRuShaBanAda vAyudEvara saduguNavuLLa tRutIya rUpagaDa |
budharige bOdhavittu tudiyalli mukuti saMpadavIva I guruvigidirArava || 12 ||
modaladu matiyeMba hanumaMtarUpugaDa idirAda pRutanege kShayavanitta |
kadanakarkasha BIma dvitIyAvatAra gaDa tudiya rUpavideMdu shruti pELitu
durmatava tuLiyitu kumatavanaLiyitu || 13 ||

saMtarmecci vidvAnmadhva ujjaBAraveMba saMtOShadi namma guruva
koMDADitu |
iMtu suprasiddha shruti tutisida madhvamuni eMthAguruvAdava nIvella nODiro
muktiya bEDirO I matava pADirO || 14 ||
madhvaneMba I vAyuve hRudguhAdoLidda ellArALda hari svAmiyeMdu
mathisuvaru gaDa |
poddi ivana pAdava Isha modalAda dEvaru buddhivaMtarAdareMdu shruti kIrtisitu
sumatavanarcisitu jnAnadIpa heccisitu || 15 ||
shruti smRutigaLa arthamathisi mADida namma kRutiyanne naMbiro nAveMdude
tatva |
matada hammanava mADadale mElaNa sadgati bEkeMbuvarellarida kELiro
eMdeMdu pELiro kumatiya kILiro aGaMgaLa sILiro || 16 ||
ella illaveMbuvana nAlage illavAyitalla inneMtu namma kUDe nuDiva |
ballavarigiMtu bOdhisi jagatu satyaveMdu nillisida madhvamunigeNegANe
iMtennade mANe shrIhariyANe || 17 ||
Iga uMTu mEgalajagadilla eMba mAtu ninagAgadalla trikAla niShEdhaveMbuvage |
kAgeyaMte oMduBAgadardhava kaMDu mattoMdu BAgava kANadiralu
kANanennare
ninnAdhamanennare nODu nODu kaNNAre || 18 ||
illi^^illavene innoMdu dEshadoLakku Iga illavene innoMdu kAladoLippudu |
elladEshavella kAladalli jagavillavenne mollana koMbinaMte kELaShTallade pokku
salladalla I vAku innu kalaha sAku || 19 ||
ballavaru satyavAgi I jagavilleMbarthavanollaralla shrutiyoLu nityaveMba padava |
illavAgi innoMdu kaDeyiMda taMdare bAyoLu kalle bILuvudalla mithyaveMba
padava
tatvavAdigAgadava unmattanInorevA || 20 ||

dvAsuparNaveMba vEda BEdhavanne pELalu sarvEshane nAneMba matadAseye
illa |
Ishatana pOdamEle AdIteMba mAtu vicAri salekUDadu ninagOsuga tanna
Ishatvavanu cennakEshava biDuvane || 21 ||
I shrutiya baladiMda Ishateya pOkaLisuvAse bEDa Isha pOdamEle shruti |
Ishanaikya pELvude avanIsha pusimAtiniMda hEsiyiMtakku anyOnyAshraya sikku
sAku sAku ninna sokku || 22 ||
aMdu BRugumuni baMdu ceMdada vakShava kAliMdalodeyalavana kuMda
nODade |
iMdirEsha tanna sarvEshvaratvava rakShisida neMdu koMDADida shrutiyiMda hariya
taMdu tannapakAriya kuMdisadeMdariya || 23 ||
kAlilla kaigaLilla karNaMgaLilla kaMgaLilla nAlageyillavenne nOva mAnava |
I lOkadi celuva kAmana geluvAkArada shrIlOlana nirAkAraneMdu pELvare
saMtarida kELvarE iMtenalu bALvare || 24 ||
guNiyallaveMba mAtu ninage hInavAdare anaMtanigImAtanennabahude |
janaru mAyAviyeMdu ninnenemuniva mAnava sanakAdimunimAnyana mAyAvi
eMbare budharida kaigoMbare bAyoLmaNNa tuMbare || 25 ||
iMta paramataveMba kaMteya paridu balu BrAMtiya biDisida guru ciMtAmaNiya |
saMtata nenedu aMtavillada padava saMtOShatIrthara kRupeyAMtaiduvenu
alli shrI mAdhavanu Iva mOdavanu || 26 ||
hattu matte nAlkulOkada jIvamottava tanna yuktiyiMda mADi
tattasthAnadaliTTa satyalOkadoDeyanaDige poDamaDuvenu ||
haritatvada bittaradarthiya tOrutirali atta itta pOgadaMte cittava tiruhutirali
muktipathadatta manava naDesutirali arthiya BRutyana BAra nityadi pottirali || 27 ||
rakkasarukka taggisidaMge dakShana shikShisidavage
yakShapatiya saKanenipa kailAsada mukkaNNagAnu kaimugivenu |
muKya manastatvABimAniyAge nInu duShkarmatati ninna kRupeyiMda nIguvenu

shuShkavAdigaLa kaMDalli naguvenu Bakuti pathavanu hitaveMdu bagevenu
nInitta jnAnadiMda muktige pOguvenu || 28 ||
sakala suraraMGrigeraguve gurugaLa vikasitavAda pAdapadumava nenedu |
niKiLajagava kAva nArAyaNana katheya BakutiyiMdAnu baNNipenu |
yukuti kOvidara kuNisuvenu aKila kujanaranu daNisuvenu |
mukutiya suKavanuNisuvenu I KaLaramatava maNisuvenu || 29 ||
iMdranna rAjyava taMdanna shuBaguNa sAMdranna surasaBA caMdranna |
naMdannakaMdanna vaMdyanna nityA naMdanna tutipe mukuMdanna || 30 ||
shauriya nenevenudAriya kujanara vairiya maMdarOddhAriya |
hariya duritanivAriya sujanOpakAriya mukutige dAriya || 31 ||
nIlanna nijajanapAlanna nirmala shIlanna sucaritra jAlanna |
bAlanna saMgItalOlanna tutipenu kAlanavarige analanna || 32 ||
iShTanna duritAGaraTTanna jagakatidiTTanna satata saMtuShTanna |
shiShTanna shuBaguNa puShTanna tutipenutkRuShTanna shrutigiMbugoTTanna || 33
||
raMganna karuNAMtaraMganna KaLakula BaMganna munijana saMganna |
aMgajAnaMgannajanaka nityashuBAMganna tutipenuttuMganna || 34 ||
shlOka - taravaH kiM na jIvaMti BastrAH kiM na shvasaMtyuta
na KAdaMti na mEhaMti kiM grAmyAHpashavOparE
balEbatOrukrama vikramAnyE na shRuNvataH karNapuTI narasya
jihvA satI dArdurikEva sUta sa cEt
pragAyatyurugAya gAthAM barhAyitE nayanE narANAM liMgAni
viShNOrnanirIkShatO yE pAdau nRuNAM tau drumajanma BAjau kShEtrANi
nAmavrajatO harEryau ||
harikathegaLa kELadava bahukAla bALdare PalavEnu kAnanada |
mara sAsira varuShavirade kAgeya pesaru ciraMjIviyenare sajjanaru || 35 ||

kArukana titti shvAsava biDade Ura nari nAyi haMdigaLu |
pUraisikoLLave tamatammudara mAragoLagAgi ramisave || 36 ||
mUShikana biladaMte harikathe kELi saMtOShisadavana karNaMgaLu |
shrIshanna kShEtrakke pOgada kAlugaLu pAShANa pratimeyaMGrigaLu || 37 ||
hariya nODada kaNNu hIliya kaNNu narahariya pADadavana jihve |
varalibaLaluva maMDUkana jihve harigeragada narane vAnaranu || 38 ||
shlOka - tavApyEtarhi kauravya saptAhaM jIvitAvadhiH |
upakalpaya tatsarvaM yattAvatsAMparAyikaM ||
KaTvAMgO nAma rAjarShijnAtvEyattAmihAyuShaH |
muhurtAssarvamutsRujya gatavAnaBayaM hariM ||
ELudina harikatheya kELi obba dALi iDane haripurake |
trilOlana nenederaDugaLigeyobba mElaNa mukutigErane || 39 ||
adariMda nArAyaNana koMDADuva budharu saMsAravanodedu |
mudadiMda vaikuMThakkaidi shrIkRuShNana padasannidhiyali suKisuvaru || 40 ||
shlOka - tatO vaikuMThamagamadBAsvaraM tamasaH paraM |
yatra nArAyaNaH sAkShAt nyAsinAM paramA gatiH ||
shAMtAnAM nyasta daMDAnAM yatO nAvartate yatiH |
vaikuMThaM nAma lOkaM taM divyaM nityaM sanAtanaM ||
sAkShAnnArAyaNanippa vaikuMThava pokku badukuvude mOkSha |
pakShapAtavalla shukamunivAkya vivEkisi nIvE nODiro || 41 ||
eMdeMdu vaikuMThalOkakke nAshavilla iMdirEshana vikuMTha |
ceMdadavana maneyenipa vaikuMThakke maMdamatiye nAshavuMTe || 42 ||
tanna mane pOdamEle nArAyaNa bannaganaMte kAnanadi |
vanniteyara kUDi paNPalava meluvane manna baMdaMte nuDivare || 43 ||

nashvaravallada I padave budharige shAshvatasnAnavenipudu |
BAsvara vaikuMThavadariMda ellarge nishcita mukuti kANiro || 44 ||
paramAM gatiyeMdu vaikuMThadarasana shrIvarana shukayOgi varNisida |
arikeyuLLa budharu adariMdI padavanne parama mukutiyennabEku || 45 ||
dhanya yatigaLI lOkava pokkamEle punarAvRutti illa gaDa |
innoMdu muKyamukuti uMTeMba KaLara manava mardisitAgi || 46 ||
na ca punarAvartate eMba vEdAMta varNisida mukutiya biTTinnoMdu |
hesarillada mukuti salladAgi namma eseva vaikuMThave mOkSha || 47 ||
pELelo vAdi tamaveMba ninna ajnAna bILukoTTu lOka pusiyE |
AlOcisiko ninna matada rahasyava I lOkave divyamukti || 48 ||
iMtu nODalu sarvapadada saMpada ninage BrAMti gaMTala gANavAytu |
haMtatanava biDu nAveMdarthavanu saMtOShadiMdaMgIkarisu || 49 ||
shlOka - vaikuMThanAma lOkOyaM divyaM nityaM sanAtanaM |
avaiShNavAnAmaprApyaM guNatrayavivarjitaM ||
nityasiddhaiH samAkIrNaM tanmayaiH pAMcakAlikaiH |
saBAprAsAda saMyuktaM vanaishpOpavanRurvRutaM ||
vApIkUpa taTAkaishca vRukShaShaMDaishca maMDitaM |
aprAkRutaM surairvaMdyaM AyutArka samapraBaM ||
prakRuShTa satvarAshiM tvAM kadAdrakShyAmi cakShuShA |
brahmalOka padAdUrdhvaM yatpuraM cakrapANinaH
gOviMda BaktirmahatAM narANAMca na saMshayaH ||
lOkaikanAtha nArAyaNage priyavAda vaikuMThapuriya varNipenu |
shrIkAMtanalli muktarige eMdeMdunirAkula suKavittu poreva || 50 ||
shrIkRuShNanaMGriya neneyadavarige I lOkaveMdeMdu dorakadu |
prakRuShTa tatvarAshigaLallippavu gaDa prAkRutavalla nityagaDa || 51 ||

eMdeMdu nitya sanAtanaveMba I ceMdada padavu divyagaDa |
niMdya triguNaMgaLu hoMdavI lOkakke kuMdukorateyilla gaDa || 52 ||
adariMda bommAdi dEvarellaru hariya sadanavenipa puratrayake |
mudadiMda kaimugidu pUjisuvareMdeMdI pada nitya siddhAspadagaDa || 53 ||
allidda vApikUpa taTAkaMgaLu mattalidda mane upparigegaLu |
ballida rame tanna nallana cittava vallisabEkeMdihaLu gaDa || 54 ||
arkakOTigaLaMte vaikuMThalOka dashadikkinoLage beLaguvudu |
lakkumigallade iMtha kAMti mikkavarige bake nIve vicArisiro || 55 ||
vaikuMThaveMba hariya lOka bommana lOkakiMtalu mElihudu |
shOkarahitarAda siddhasAdhyaralli bEkAda suKavanuNutiharu || 56 ||
lakShayOjana mElakkanaMtAsana lakShmIshaniha shvEtadvIpa |
lakSha^^aivattu vaikuMTha ippattaidu lakShaShODaSha kOTiyallihudu || 57 ||
shlOka - savai mahABAgavataHparIkShidyEnApavargAKya madaBra buddhiH |
jnAnEna vaiyAsaki shabditEna BEjE KagEMdradhvaja pAdamUlaM ||
jnAnasAdhyavAda muKya muktisthAna shrInAthaniha vaikuMTha |
yEnApavargAKyaM eMba BAgavatOkti tAne nirNaisi pELitala || 58 ||
ide apavargaveMdu vyAsadEvanolidu pELida hariya pAdave mOkSha |
adhamavAdigaLige idu kELi cittada madavaLivudu EnAshcarya || 59 ||
nADa KODigaLu vyAsavacana naMbade mUDhagarvaru guruvenipa |
prauDharige sammatavAda vyAsara mAtanODi mannisadire nagare || 60 ||
BEjE KagEMdra dhvaja pAda mUlameMdI jagatKyAta BAgavata |
OjeyiMdali pELitAgi anyara mata rAjipudeMtu saBeyoLage || 61 ||

pELelo vAdi KagEMdradhvajapAda mUla ninna muktiyoLuMTe |
I liMga harilOkakke sAdhAraNaveMdu bAlakarellarballaraise || 62 ||
alli kRuShNana pAdasEveye kaivalyavallade avanaikya salla |
ellaru ballaru hariya BEdavallade^^illaveMbudanu || 63 ||
KageMdranAmave alli taratama BAva bageyanaruhitu pAdashabda |
BagavAn sAkAraneMdu vyAsOktige kAma dhEnUkti pratiye || 64 ||
shlOka - na vartatE yatra rajastamastyayaHsatvaM ca mishraM na ca kAlavikramaH |
na yatra mAyA kimutAparE harEranuvratA yatra surAsurArcitAH ||
muktiyoLiha BEda satyaveMbudu siddha matte na yatra mAyA eMba |
yatra BAgavatOkti muktara BEdava satyaveMdu sthApisitalla || 65 ||
‘harEranuvratAyatra’veMbIsmRuti nirUpisitu hariya BEda |
paramArtha satya ninagU adE mAye irade kalpitavahude || 66 ||
IShanmAye ire yatramAyA nEti vyAsana sAmAnya niShEdha |
pusi kUDuvude puTTida GaTaviralu nAstyatra GaTaveMdennuvare || 67 ||
ninnicCege bEkAdartha pELvude shabda tanna shaktyarthava toredu |
ennabahudaise tuhinapara shabda vahniyarthavanu nuDivude || 68 ||
shlOka - tanmadhyE nagarI divyA sAyOdhyEti prakIrtitA |
ArUDhayauvanairnityA divyanArI narairyutA ||
ratna kettisida cinnadELu kOTe manmathanayyana purige |
tanmadhyadalli ayOdhyAnagarige suvarNagOpuravopputihudu || 69 ||
siridEvi tAne muraharana paTTaNadoLu paripariya maneya rUpadali |
mirimiri miMcuvaLu Acala prakRutiyiMda viracita gRuhagaLalliravu || 70 ||

shlOka - natadBbAsayatE sUryO na shashAMkO na pAvakaH |
yadgatvAnanivartaMtE taddhAma paramaM mama ||
anarGya ratna maMdiradupparigegaLa baNNisalennaLavalla |
rannadA dvAra praKara kAMtige tanniMtAne ODuvudaMdhakAra || 71 ||
‘ayutArka samapraBA’ eMba paMcarAtra Bayavilladacyutana purava |
priyadiMda koMDADitAgi A pura kattaleya keDisuvudoMdaccariye || 72 ||
nAlkudikkugaLali bAgila sAlgaLu cauka shuddhada kOTeyoLage |
lOkapAlakara mannaNeyiMdalallige shrIkAMtanommomme bAha || 73 ||
‘sa^^EnAnbrahmagamayati’ eMbashruti nayadiMda nirNaisitAgi |
priyavAda liMgadEhada jIvanmuktaru jayajayavenutiharalli || 74 ||
apratIkAlaMbanaranu muKyaprANa sapta prAkAraMgaLoLage |
muktipariyaMta BOgaMgaLuMDukoMDippaMte kaTTumADuvanu || 75 ||
muktAmuktaru kUDi adariMda beresiharu sapta prAkAraMgaLoLage |
citra cAvaDiyoLu allidda harige A mukta suraru binnaisuvaru || 76 ||
muktarige maneyAda hariyaMtaHpurada suttalippudu virajAnadiyu |
tatvajnAnigaLu adaroLage muLuge nirmuktavAhudu liMgadEha || 77 ||
shlOka - pradhAnaparama vyOmnOraMtarA virajAnadI
dEvAMga svEda janitA tOyaiHprasravitA shuBA
shrEyO mOkShapadaM divyaM amRutaM viShNumaMdiraM
akSharaM paramaM dhAma vaikuMThaM shAshvataM padaM
nityaMca paramavyOma sarvOtkRuShTaM sanAtanaM
paryAya vAcakAstasya paraMdhAmnOcyutasya ca
saptamadvAra pariyaMta baMdhaka mAye matte muktiyoLippa hariya |
uttamAMtaHpuradiMteraDara naDuve suttalippudu virajAnadiyu || 78 ||

ELane bAgiloLidda jayavijayaru BUlOkadali puTTidarAgi |
kAlanaBayavIva prakRuti A pariyaMta kAlUri janara kaTTuvaLu || 79 ||
adariMdoLage muktarpOguvarallade mikka budharige saMcAra salla |
adukAraNa nArAyaNanE baMdallige mudavitta sanakAdigaLige || 80 ||
hariyaMtarnagarige paramaM vyOma nAma horagidda prakRutiyE pradhAna |
purANaMgaLadariMda pradhAna paramavyOmAM taradi virajeyeMdoredavu || 81 ||
hariyaMgadoLagidda bevarUdakavAgi siridEvi tAne poramaTTu |
harivaLu rajashabda sUcita guNatraya virada kAraNa virajeyenipaLu || 82 ||
lekkavillada muktiyOgya jIvaranu musukirda prakRutiya keDisuva |
shaktiyatyuktige hariyaMgasaMgada udakkavAdaLu lakShmIdEvi || 83 ||
shlOka - niH shrEyasaM ca nirvANaM kaivalyaM mOkSha ucyatE |
nAnA jAti samAkIrNaM vaikuMThaM taddharEH padaM ||
virajeyoLagaNa paTTaNadoLu muktaru viriMcAdi suraru mAnavaru |
tarupakShi modalAda nAnA jAtigaLiharidara praBe tamagiMbugoDadu || 84 ||
jAti hInareMdu nIkarisadiri shrIpati matsya kUrma AkRutiyiM |
KyAtanAgire ballavaru A rUpagaLa Otu mannisi tutisuvaru || 85 ||
belladacciniMda mADida kAsAra sallade balla budharige |
kalleMdu biDuvare mANikyaratnava allidda jAti shOBanavu || 86 ||
uraga garuDa haMsa mahiSha mESha vRuShaBa kari makari turagagaLu |
surariMda mannisikoLave shAma shabaLa nararella niruta pUjisarE || 87 ||
uttara lOkada nAnA jAtigaLige uttamateyu tappadenalu |
cittina putthaLiyAgi muktiyoLirda citrajAtiya baNNisuvenu || 88 ||

shlOka - sarvE naMdaMti yashasAgatEna saBA sAhEna saKyA saKAyaH
kilbiSha spRutpituShaNirhyEShAmaraM hitOBavati vAjinAya
RucAMtva H pOShamAstE pupuShvAn
gAyatraM tvO gAyati shakvarIShu
brahmAtvO vadati jAta vidyAM
yajnasya mAtrAM vimimIta utva H
yata brahmApavamAna CaMdasyAM vAcaMvadan ityAdi vEdavE |
muktiyallippa brahmAdijIvara vartaneyanu varNisutalidako || 89 ||
haripuradoLagippa sakalamuktarugaLa irava baNNasi pogaLuva |
sarvEnaMdaMti ityAdishrutyarthava orevenu kELi sajjanaru || 90 ||
hRudayada pApava toLeva annavanIva padumanABanu muktarugaLa |
kudureyaMte kuNiva kaNge gOcaranAgi odagikoDuva suKaMgaLanu || 91 ||
allalle pADuva muktara saBegaLa ullAsa kaMDu tA tiLiva |
ballida yashavuLLa hariyeMba satheyiMda ella muktaru suKisuvaru || 92 ||
obba brahmanu RugvEdava GOShisuva gaDa obba gAyatri sAmavanu |
ubbida manadiMda gAnava mADuva mattobba brahmanu purANagaLa || 93 ||
abjanABana puradi Odutippanu gaDa obba shrIhariya mUrtiyannu |
abbaradi nenedu suKisuvanu gaDa obba brahmanu sOmarasava || 94 ||
abjanABanigagni muKadi koDuva gaDa obba brahmanu pUjisuva gaDa |
sarbadEvategaLu I pariyalli hariya garBavAsadalli iharu || 95 ||
iMtanaMta brahmAdyaru vaikuMThadalli aMtaraMtadalihareMdu |
maMtragaLu koMDADutive adariMda shrIkAMtana mahimegEneMbe || 96 ||
manOjavEShvA samAbaBUvuH eMba cinumayarAda muktarigU |
anuBavisuva AnaMdAdigaLa tAratamyavanu shruti tAne pELitalla || 97 ||

adariMda bommapaTTadavarellaranu modalige nenedavara ceMda |
padaviya bEre koMDADitu shruti mattuLidavaranoMdAgi tutisitu || 98 ||
hariyaramaneya vAlagashAlegaitappa viriMcirAshige lekkavilla |
terateradali bappa garuDEMdra caMdrAdi surara tiMtiNiyanEneMbe || 99 ||
puTTamuniya poTTeyaMbudhijalakiMbugoTTitenalu sarvEshvarana |
paTTadaramaneya cAvaDi baMda baMdaShTu muktarige tAniMbukoDadE || 100 ||
oMdoMdu kalpadali muktarAdamararu ceMda ceMdadalallalliharu |
iMdireyOlagadi vANimodalAda iMdumuKiyaroppiharu || 101 ||
avara lAvaNyava avara tAruNyava avaruTTa citrAMbarava |
avara sarvAMga divyABaraNaMgaLa vivaravanAva baNNisuva || 102 ||
shlOka - idaM jnAnamupAshritya mama sAdharmyamAgatAH |
sargEpi nOpajAyaMtE praLayE na vyathaMti ca ||
sarvEcaturbAhava unmiShanmaNi pravEka niShkABaraNAH suvarcasaH |
pravALa vaiDhUrya mRuNAla varcasaH parisPpuratkuMDalamauLi mAlinaH ||
iTTa makuTaMgaLa toTTaMgitOLgaLavaTTa sara hAra padakagaLa |
uTTa poMbaTTegaLa kaMkaNAMgadagaLa meTTida ponna pAvugeya || 103 ||
poLeva kuMDalagaLu uliva kiMkiNigaLu naLanaLisuva nyAvaLagaLu |
naliva aMdugegaLu muktara divyAMga celuvanadAva varNisuva || 104 ||
karacatuShTayada muktaru kRuShNanoDanalli sariberesiha samayadalli |
urada sirivatsa kaustuBada kuruhu kaMDu hariyivaneMdarivaru gaDa || 105 ||
viriMci kaimugiyalu garuDanEri baralu uragana maMcadoLiralu |
arivaru alladirdoDe sArUpyada mukti terevaDisi nODalIyadu gaDa || 106 ||
sAyujya sAlOkya sAmIpya sArUpya IyaMda caturvidhamukti |
hEya liMgadEha pOda mElavaravara svAyOgyateyiMdoppuvudu || 107 ||

shrIkAMtanaMgava muTTikoMDippude bEkAda sAyujyamukti |
I kujanareMbaikyava yujiryOgE eMba vyAkaraNOkti biDisitalla || 108 ||
hariyaMgavAshraisi allippa avara paragatiyadara mEle muktiyoLu |
terateradalli sirimUrtiyalipparAgIpari surarE sAyujyArharu || 109 ||
idda muktigaLalli BEda uMTeMbudu siddha sakala vAdigaLigu |
shabdOktiyiMdali BEdabaMditAgi biddu hOyitu parasiddhAMtavu || 110 ||
sAlOkya harilOkadoLage tuMbippude AlOkad~hattili sutta |
pAlasAgaradalli suKisuva jIvara pAlige sAmIpyakANirO || 111 ||
shrIvatsakaustuBa horatAgi hariyaMte AvAga karacatuShTayadi |
pAvana shaMKacakrAdigaLa dharisiha jIvarge sArUpya mukti || 112 ||
sArUpyaveMbOdu sarvarigu sari eMdu mUrumuktiyiMda horage |
sArUpyamukuteMdu piriyaru karevaru bErebEravarigiravu gaDa || 113 ||
mUru shAkava mADi lavaNa kUDisidaru mUru shAkaveMdu karevaraise |
bErebaDisida lavaNa lavaNaveMdenipudu I rItiyahudu sArUpya || 114 ||
shrIlOlanAjne I satyalOkagaLalli nelesidaMtha mukutarige |
Alasya hasi tRuShe kAlakarmada kOTalegaLu tuDukalammavu gaDa || 115 ||
divyaBOgaMgaLa lIleyiMduMbuvaru divyagItegaLa pADuvaru |
divyagaMdha parimaLaMgaLa pUsuvaru divyanArI nararalli || 116 ||
jyOtirmayada heNNugaMDugaLu aprAkRuta dEhagaLalli ihavu |
prItiyiMdommomme avaroLu pokku nAnA teradali suKisuvaru || 117 ||
muktara BOgakke takka PalaMgaLa hottuhottige koDutippa |
nityAprAkRutavAda citravRukShagaLalli suttamuttaloppihavu || 118 ||

nityanirduHKa suKasvarUparAgi sutta suLivaru lIleyalli |
nityAprAkRuka PalaMgaLavarge suKavanittu matte munniddalle ihavu || 119 ||
idu citravalla tuMDrisi shAKaMgaLa mADi kudisi viprarge uNNisida |
cadura vAtApi tammaNNa karedAgale modalinaMte bAha kaMDya || 120 ||
shlOka - BrAjiShNuBiryaH paritO virAjatE lasadvima nAvaLiBirmahAtmanAM |
vidyOtamAna pramadOttamABiH savidyudaBrAvaLiBiryathA naBaH ||
oppuva vimAnavEri merevaru kaMdarpana kELiyalliharu |
tapparu dharmamArgavanu adharma tolagippudu avara svaBAva || 121 ||
citradi bareda heNNugaMDaMte anya strIyaralli muktarige |
cittaveragadu tammatamma strIyaralli arthiya mADuvaraise || 122 ||
tAya sobaga kaMDakaMDAga makkaLu nyAyapathavanu biDuvare |
shrIyiMda miMcuva magaLa kaMDare pita kAyajasharakoLagAguvane || 123 ||
celuva taMgiya kaMDaroDahuTTidaramana vaLukuvude pApapathake |
kaligoLagAdavarigI mArgavire nirmala muktarige drOha bahude || 124 ||
shlOka - AnaMdAnmaMdamaMdA dadati hi marutaH
kuMda maMdAra naMdyAvartAmOdAn dadhAnA
mRudupadamuditOdgItakaiH suMdarINAM
vRuMdairAvaMdya muktEMdvahimagu madanA
hIMdra dEvEMdrasEvyE maukuMdE
maMdirEsmannaviratamudayanmOdinAM dEvadEva
kuMdamaMdAra mallige naMdAvartAra viMdadalleseva sauraBada |
gaMdhavAhananalli bIsuva muktarAnaMdakke nitya suKavIva || 125 ||
caMdanada rasa pUsida maiyoLu hoMdida mOda shaityavane |
maMdamAruta baMdu vyaktamADisuvadariMda muktara BOgagaLigE || 126 ||

matta nartanadaMte shakta nRupAlage BRutyana kailAginaMte |
muktara BOgaMgaLappuvu hariyalli citracAritralIlegaLu || 127 ||
nityatRuptanu kRutakRutyanaccuta gaDa muktarella prakAmaru gaDa |
itta ivarATava atta shrutipAThava vyarthamADadava jANa || 128 ||
adariMda tamma nityAnaMda tapadaMtodagida viShayarAshigaLa |
madananayyana puradoLagidda muktaru mudadiMda sEviparaise || 129 ||
ara eMdu Nya eMdu alli sudhesAgaraveraDeMdeMdippuvugaDa |
sarasa lIleyiMda adara rasavanu muktaru baMdAsvAdisuvaru gaDa || 130 ||
oMdu ashvatthavu ceMdadamRutarasava eMdeMdu kareyutippudu gaDa |
baMdadanommomme mukutaru tamma mana baMdaMtAsvAdisuvaru gaDa || 131 ||
shuddhaprAkRutavAda ShaDvidha rasavuLLa svAdvannagaLa koDutippa |
hRudyanadigaLu sutta parivuvu padmanABana puradoLage || 132 ||
sarpipAyasaveMba kardamaMgaLa kUDi oppuva BakShyaBOjyagaLa |
tOrpa amyatanadigaLalli parivudanoppugoMbaru lEleyiMda || 133 ||
vApi kUpa taTAkaMgaLihavu nAnA Palaverasida tarugaLu |
tOpugaLalli ommomme ivaru nAnApari krIDeyADuvaru || 134 ||
nityAprAkRutavAda caturavidhannagaLiM tuttanommomme sEviparu |
sattigeviDivaru cAmaraMgaLanalli BRutyaravarige bIsuvaru || 135 ||
makkaLettikoMba tAyi suKadiMda ukkuvaMtalli sEvipara |
BaktiBaritacitta ubbikobbidare sauKyAbdhiyu tuLukuvudaise || 136 ||
pAluMba savigiMda sakkaregUDida pAlukuDiva suKa mElu |
lOlAkShiyara nOLva suKadiMdavaraMgadAliMganada suKa mElu || 137 ||

iMtu mahaMtara suKamElu muktiyoLaMtaraMtaradi sEvipara |
saMtOSha tAratamyadalippudeMdu vEdAMtadi hayavadananoreda || 138 ||
vaikuMThaveMdeMba tanna purakatheya parAkuviTTu kELuvara |
shrIkAMta kAvaneMballi modala saMdhi I kAvyadoLage mugiyitu || 139 ||
shrIdhara hayavadanarAyana dayadiMda vAdirAjEMdra racisida |
I divyakAvyadi muktiyoreva ramya vAda modalasaMdhi posabage || 140 ||
-sRuShTi saMdhiidu puNyakathe lOkakkide mukutiya patha ida kELuvavane kRutArtha |
idu sarvasAdhana vidhugaLige sammata mudavanIvudu kELva janake || 1 ||
shlOka - AsIdEkO ha vaicAtra viShNurnArAyaNAhvayaH |
na brahmA na ca rudrashca na dEvA na maharShayaH ||
obba nArAyaNane layadallippanu gaDa abjasaMBavanAgalliranu |
abbarada rudra mattirda dEvarkaLu sarba^^RuShigaLallilla gaDa || 2 ||
EkO nArAyaNa AsIdeMba shruti shrIkRuShNanobbane praLayadali |
A kAladi na brahmA naca shaMkara eMdu bEkAdarthava nirNaisitalla || 3 ||
shlOka - saMhRutya niKilaM shEtE nidrayA praLayAMbuni |
kadApi na viyujyOta tvayA vishvapatiH sadA ||
praLayakAladali ella jagava layava mADi lalane lakShmikUDe vaTada |
eleyalli malagi suKadallippa eMdu aLivilla prakRuti puruSharge || 4 ||
samanA eMba sUtra prakRutishabda vAcya ramegU tatpuruSha shrIharigU |
samadEsha kAlagaLallirava pELitAgi Brame salla nAveMdarthadalli || 5 ||
bommana praLayadali summaneyAgippa namma dEvage mRutyuvilla |
janmavivage illa prAgaBAvavilla ammamma mRuNmayavahude || 6 ||

janana maraNagaLa toredAlayadi hari vaniteyaroDanADuvAga |
manemanedaivaMgaLelli pOdavo sarvAgraNi bommahemmaganu || 7 ||
anEka danujaraTTuLi baMdabaMdAga anusarisi ivana eMdeMdU |
anAyAsadalli bALva dEvara hari geNe^^eMbaravivEkigaLu || 8 ||
pAraMtakAlE sarvE muccaMti eMba niravakAsha shrutiyiralu |
durAseya biDu vAdi innoMdu layadi viriMci praLayave mahApraLaya || 9 ||
I layakkaLukada kAraNa hariguNagaLige laya salladAgi |
tALadu nirguNa nirAkArada mAtu AlOcaneya ballavarige || 10 ||
Ekanenipa brahma[gai]kyaveMtappudu EkavE aikyavallavallA |
EkasyaBAva aikyaveMdu pELvare vyAkaraNadavara nI kELo || 11 ||
dharmavenipa nimma brahma jIvaraikya cinmAtradali advitIya |
ammamma advitIya shrutiyu ninage sammataikyava KaMDisitalla || 12 ||
tanna bAyige muTTutiha mUShakana biTTu ninna shrutiyeMba Bujaganu |
anyatra pOgade oMdariMdudara saMpUrNavAgalu matteragadu || 13 ||
lOkavilleMbAga lOkAMtargatavAdI vAku tAnE pOgadihudE |
tA keDuvarthava tAnakaTa pELvare kAkumADadiru shrutigaLa || 14 ||
shrutavAdarthavA shrutiyanne keDisuva pAtakavaM gaisuvudE |
yAtariMdEnAytu tadviGAtakke hEtuvalleMbaru budharu || 15 ||
cinmAtrAshrayaveMba nimma ajnAnavu namma nArAyaNagilla |
rammeyarasa tanna nABipadmadiMda nirmisidI jagapusiyE || 16 ||
anAdimAyA suptanu gaDa jIvanu anidragaDa parabomma |
anuBavake taMduko I shrutiyarthava manake baMdaMtADabEDa || 17 ||

mRutiyilladava nityAmRutaneMdu prasiddha kRutiyilladava punarBavake |
atidUranallave adariMda namma shrIpati nityamukta ballavage || 18 ||
ava nityamukta jIvaru madhyamuktareMba viruddhadharma muktiyoLu |
suvivEkigaLige sammatavAdakAraNa ivanaikyavalliyu salla || 19 ||
eMdeMdu karNashUnya pannaganigu kaLuviniMda karNa pOdavagu |
maMdamAnava mahadaMtaravallave IyaMda madhyamamukutarigu || 20 ||
sAyujyaveMba shabdavu shAbdikarige[yujiryOgE]eMba dhAtuviniM- |
dAyiteMbudu siddhavadariMda bAyige bIgavAyitalla KaLara || 21 ||
hariya sarvAMgadi tuMbirda jIvara irave sAyujyavenipudu |
maruLAgabEDa mAnava sarvEshanetta hariyanuvratamuktaretta || 22 ||
shlOka - kShyEhi cEtanagaNAn suKaduHKamadhya |
saMprAptayE tanuBRutAM vihRutiM mamEcCan ||
sO#0073;yaM vihAra ihamE tanuBRutsvaBAva |
saMBUtayE Bavati BUtakRudEva BUtyAH ||
mattoMdu taMDada jIvarAshigaLige mukti modalAda gatiya |
cittajanayya [ittape]neMdu punarapi citra jagattu nirmisida || 23 ||
idu lIle tanage lakShmige mahadaishvaryadAspadava koDuvudu jIvarige |
sadA sammishra PalavAhudu adariMda aduButa jagava nirmisida || 24 ||
lOhita shukla kRuShNagaLenipa prakRutiya nEhada nijasatigittu |
shrI hariyadariMda varNatrayada rENu vyUhava bEre bEriTTa || 25 ||
satvaveMba guNa shuklANugaLa rAshi raktANuve rajOguNavu |
matte nIlANugaLa mottave tamOguNa pratyEka shaktigaLivake || 26 ||
I paramANugaLa rUpaveMbO guNada vyApAra bahaLavAgiralu |
A paramANugaLa guNaveMdu karevarai tApasaridake meccuvaru || 27 ||

yAvadravya BAviguNake guNiyoLEkIBAvaveMdeMba rahasya |
kOvidarige tOruvudu I guNagaLane BAvajna guNaveMdeMbuvaru || 28 ||
ippattunAlku I tatvasUkShmaMgaLige tappade sthaulya bappaMte |
oppuvI guNatrayadaNugaLa kUDisi sarpashAyi sRuShTisuva || 29 ||
beresida ippattu nAlku tattvaMgaLa parama sUkShmANu rAshigaLa |
terateradi tegedu tattvaMgaLa sAla viracisuvaMda sAlade || 30 ||
eShTu mahattatva sRuShTigAgabEko aShTu triguNada aMshagaLa |
iTTu mattadariMda ahaMkAratatvava puTTisuvudakkoMdiShTiDuva || 31 ||
kAraNa tatvarAshigaLiMda tegetegedu bEridda triguNadaMshagaLa |
sErisi uttarOttaratattvaMgaLa shrIdhara mADuva kramadiMda || 32 ||
mahatteMba tatva mahimeyanIvudu ahaM tatvadiMdahaMkAra |
bAhOdu buddhi nishcaisikoDuvudu nAnAhaMbalikeya manavu || 33 ||
aidu karmEMdriyagaLaidu jnAnEMdriyagaLaidu tanmAtra tatvagaLu |
aidu BUtaMgaLeMdippattunAlaku AdikAlada tatvaMgaLu || 34 ||
hattu karaNaMgaLu nityadi viShayagaLa artiya tOri I manava |
attaleLeyalu uMDuMDahaMkarise martyarige bahade mahatva || 35 ||
nitya naimittika satkarmaMgaLa mareduttamaroLu matsarisuva |
vitta saMpattigunmattanAgi Bavadali sutti sutti artiyanuMba || 36 ||
aMganeyarAsege caraNaMgaLu naDesuvuvu kaMgaLavaraMgava tOruvuvu |
baMgArakoDisyavara eMjalanuNisuvuvu karNaMgaLu nuDige maruLahavu || 37 ||
duShTAnna uMDuMDu poTTeporeyisuvu[vu] BraShTaroDanADisuvuvu |
koTTare koMDADi koDadire baisuvuvu kaShTagatige kaDegeLasuvuvu || 38 ||

I tattvaMgaLigIsharAda dEvategaLa vrAtagaLanivu keDisavu |
BUtaLadoLagarasinamanesaMkOle Atana kAla kaTTuvude || 39 ||
jIvarAshigaLigI tatvagaLiMdale nOvanIvuta BavadoLage |
tAvidakkoLagAgadiharu shrIhariya kRupAvalOkana baladiMda || 40 ||
iMtu BrAMtiyanIva I tatvaMgaLe mahaMtara saMga dorakalu |
saMtata shravaNAdi sanmArgakkeragisi kaMtupitana tOrisuvuvu || 41 ||
hariyatta naDesuvuvu harinAma nuDisuvuvu haripUjeyane mADisuvuvu |
harimUrti nODisi harikIrti pADisi nararahaMkRuti keDisuvuvu || 42 ||
ukku taggisuvuvu sokku nivArisi satkarmakikki salahuvuvu |
duHKavIva paMcaBUtmAtmaka dEhadakkara biDisi rakShipuvu || 43 ||
Isu puNyava mADi dinadina dhEnise shrIsha saMtOShisi tanna |
BAsuramUrtiya kaNge kANisikoDuva dOShagaLa dUrakkODisuva || 44 ||
aMtavillada svarUpasuKadanuBavake aMtarAyava mALpaveMdu |
ciMtisi tudiyoLiva saMtarisuvaMte shrIkAMtanna saMtarbEDuvaru || 45 ||
kaNNaMsha kANOdu kiviyaMsha kELOdu rasanaMshAsvAdisuvudu |
BinnatattvagaLige BinnaBinnakAryavanne mADuva shakti kANiro || 46 ||
anyOnya kAryava mADalariyavu caraNa naDedaMte kai naDeyuvude |
GrANa gaMdhavAGrANisuvaMte tvagaMsha GrANisaballude kELi || 47 ||
iMbukoDuvudakke aMbarave bEku bAyituMbyUduvare vAyu bEku- |
uMbaDugege kiccubEku tRuShegaLevare aMbuve bEkuNalanna bEku || 48 ||
adariMda ippattunAlku tatvaMgaLige adhika nyUna saMKyA salla
idanu vivEkisi hari kaMDu avaravariMmodale rAshigaLa sRujisuva || 49 ||

iMtu tatva sUkShmAMsha prakRutiyoLanaMtagaLAgippuvu gaDa |
aMtha rAshigaLa nAnAdhAnyada rAshiyaMte kUDi sRuShTisuva || 50 ||
idaroLu modalu mahattatvAMshada sRuShTi adariM mEle kramakramadi |
