ahudadara shuklANugaLiMda buddhiyu manalOhitAMshagaLiM dashEMdriyagaLu ||
52 ||
kappinaMshagaLiMda paMcaBUtagaLu kalpaneyalla piriyaru |
oppi pELuvariMtu buddhiyoDane mana koppa ShODasha kalegaLa || 53 ||
tAmasaveMba kappinaMshadiMda paMcatanmAtra sRuShTi modalu gaDa |
AmEle vyOmAdi paMcaBUtagaLa janma eMbOdu siddhAMta || 54 ||
tudiyoLu sRuShTisidippattumUrane udakaveMba tattvadoLage |
kadaDadaMte BUrajavamADi kUDaliMtudisidavaKiLa tatvagaLu || 55 ||
iMtha mahadAdi tatvagaLa sRuShTisi tattasthAnadaliTTu poreva |
uttamapuruSha avara tettiganAgisutta surara nirmisidanu || 56 ||
shuddha satvaguNadiMdale tatvaMgaLALda dEvara dEhaMgaLanu |
mALdanavaravara yOgyatege takkaShTu kUDDa mikka suguNaMgaLanu || 57 ||
matte tannarasiyoDane nIroLmalagiddu tatvadoMdoMdaMshagaLanu |
citrarEtava mADi cinnadajAMDava satyasaMkalpa nirmisida || 58 ||
nIroLagidda BUrENugaLellava sErisi tannudaradoLu
Araneya garBadiM yOnidvAradi tegedu nIrajajAMDava nirmisida || 59 ||
nUrukOTiyOjana pramANa suttalu sUriyanaMte shOBisuva |
A ramya bommAMDa pokku punarapi nIroLu kRuShNa malagidda || 60 ||

bommAMDadoLage ippattunAlku tattva summanavAgi beresihavu |
AmEle BUmyAdi hattAvaraNaMgaLu krammadi suttamuttihavu || 61 ||
pRuthvirUpavAda aMDaveMbAvaraNa suttalu suttikoMDihudu |
matte appAdi satvaMtavAdAvaraNa hattu hattAgi beLedihavu || 62 ||
beLeda ThAvinalli mEl^^mElAdAvaraNa uLida tattvavanoLageLedu |
oLage horage ella beresikoMDippudiMtilladire mahimeyeMtippudidake || 63 ||
uttarOttaratatvakkadhika vyApti bEku suttu suttihudaise enalu |
tatvamayavAda dEhaMgaLeMtippuvu jIvara triguNaMgaLeMtu kaTTuvuvu || 64 ||
oLahorage vyAptavAgihavu mElaNatatva keLakeLage kILu tattvagaLihavu |
jalajanABaniMtu hattAvaraNaMgaLa oLage I jagava nirmisida || 65 ||
nUrukOTiyOjana modalaMDAvaraNakke nIramEle IrELAgi |
tOruva lOkagaLiMdaivattu kOTi mElAru mUru dashOttaravu || 66 ||
iMtellava kUDi vyAptavAda lakumikAMtana divya shrImUrti |
AMtukoMDippudu rOmakUpava tuMbuvaMte A hariginnAreduru || 67 ||
aMDOdakadi sAsiravarSha pariyaMta puMDarIkAkSha pavaDisida |
caMDAMshu sahasra sanniBanABiyiMduddaMDa kamalava nirmisida || 68 ||
ippattaidukOTi yOjana beLaguva tatpadmadalli padmajana |
kalpisi A padmadaLadalli IrELAgippa lOkagaLa mADidanu || 69 ||
modalA brahmanige muktipadavanittuLidada muKyaprANanige |
padumasaMBavaneMba paTTavanittu I hadinAlku lOkavanALeMda || 70 ||
shlOka - muKyaprANAya namO maMtratraya japaH sadA |
anugrahAya mE viShNOH prItayE kriyatE hi saH ||
