ArunUru kUDi ippattoMdusAvira maMtraika shvAsajapava |
mAruta IrELu lOkada jIvaroLOraMte mADi meccisuva || 71 ||
iMtha Baktanige brahmapaTTavanu shrIkAMta kaTTuvudoMdaccariye |
eMteMtu sEviparaMtaMtavara dayavaMtananaMta rakShisane || 72 ||
ArutiMgaLu tapamADida dhruvanige sErisidanu dhruvapadava |
nUru brahmana varuShapariyaMta I vidhadi ArAdhisidaMtha Bakutanige || 73 ||
pUraisikoDuvudake kaDeyillada RuNa sAsirakoMdu koTTu tidduvaMte |
mArutage brahmapadavittu mattavage tannArOgaNeyiMdardha yIva || 74 ||
lekkavillada nAnAjIvaru mADuva satkarmaMgaLa PalavAda |
sauKyava bommapaTTavanALva dEvana lakShmIsha kUDikoMDuMba || 75 ||
adariMda sahaBOgapadaveMba iMthA saMpadavIva muKyaprANanige |
madananayyaniMtu mADida sEvege sadRusha PalaviMtu koDuva || 76 ||
naMbida sAliga baMdu baMdu bEDaluMbAga kUDikoMDuMDu |
naMbisuvaMte bommanigardha uNisi hara uMba saMBramavanEneMbe || 77 ||
bommana nUruvaruSha pariyaMta sammIra mADida japake |
sammAna PalavoMdu brahmakalpadaluNisi rammEsha tAneMdeMduMba || 78 ||
