taveyAda suKagaLa tannavarige koTTu javana bAdhegaLa biDisida || 5 ||
haLeyaMgigaLa kaLedu celuva citrAMbarada poLevaMgigaLa toDuvaMte |
jalajAkSha mADuva layada lIleyu mukti PalavIvududariMda tutipe || 6 ||
jagava pAlisi mattIjaga[da jIvarge] bagebageya gatigaLa koDalu |
magana nUruvaruSha mugiyalu munnirdaMte BagavAn layake manavitta || 7 ||
shlOka - naShTE lOkE dviparArdhAvasAnE mahABUtEShvAdiBUtaM gatEShu |
vyaktEvyaktaM kAlavEgEna nItE BavAnEkaH shiShyatEshEShasaM~g~jaH ||

pAtALa modalAda lOkava praLayadi vAtasaKaniMdali suDisi |
BUtapaMcaka modalAda tatvaMgaLa shrInAtha saMharisidAkShaNadi || 8 ||
mUruguNaMgaLa mUlaprakRutiyalli sErisi sarvajIvaranu |
kAraNapuruSha tanna kukShiyoLiTTu shrIramaNige suKavitta || 9 ||
atta mahattatvavALda dEhaviralu citrajIvara mottagaLanu |
hottiha satyalOkada brahma virajeya tIrthasnAnake[salvanalla] || 10 ||
adariMda ippattumUru tattvaMgaLa adhipatigaLa kUDikoMDu |
modala tattva tanna mUlarUpadi kUDi madananayyage tuttanitta || 11 ||
hiMde brahmana sRujisi avanaMgavanAgale tiMdare tuttu kuMduvudu |
eMdudAsInava mADida shrIkRuShNa iMdu BuMjisi tEgutirda || 12 ||
saptadvIpagaLalli suttamuttalippa BaktarAshige gaNaneyilla |
arthiya BakShakke takka dhAnyaMgaLa motta parvatadaMtittu || 13 ||
nAnAPalaMgaLu nAnApakvAnnagaLu nAnAvidhada shAkaMgaLu |
nAnA kaMdamUlagaLu shrIkRuShNanna AnaMdakkaMdodagidavu || 14 ||
shruti : yasya brahma ca kShatraM cOBE Bavata OdanaH |
mRutyuryasyOpasEcanaM ka itthAvEda yatrasaH ||
heDataleya mRutyuvE aDigaDige tuppavAyitoDaloMdoMd^^eMbOde |
tuttugaLAduvu jaDatanavillada jagadoDeyanittu mAreDe
baDisidaMte BuMjisuva gaDa || 15 ||
madhukaiTaBareMba kobbida dAnavara maiyoLu hudugippa rUparasagaMdha
Barita |
vEdadiMda mADida I mEdini shrIdharage svAduvAda mAMsavAyitu || 16 ||
ELukOTiyOjana pramANadi beLedu tannoLage nAnAvidha prANagaLa tuMbirda |
kalimala kaLeva I iLeye nammacyutage poLeva puNyAmiShavAyitu kANiro || 17 ||

dEva pUrvadEva upadEva BUmidEva dhanavIva rAyadEva modalAda jIvara |
pAvanavAda vyAdhiyillada I dEhagaLe BAvanekoTTaMte BavyAmiShavAyitu || 18 ||
ELu sAgaradoLu tuMbirda jalacara jAlaMgaLige lekkavilla |
sAlAgi vanavanadi saMcarisuva mRugavyALOragagaLa baNNipenu || 19 ||
AdipuruShaniMtu tanna BOjanakke sAdhanavAda dravyagaLa |
shrIdEvi tAne svayaMpAkiyaLaMte A layajvAle kiccinali || 20 ||
lavaNEkShumadhusarpidadhikShIragaLa rasava kUDi haimAMDaveMba |
taveyada BAMDadoLiTTu pAkava mADi tavakadiMdoMdu tuttAgi || 21 ||
Buvana vyAptavAda sthUladEhada bAyavivarava tegedu BuMjisida |
pavana tanayyanuMba saMBramake maibevaradaMtaDigaDige bIse || 22 ||
navashuddhadArNava jalaveMba pAnIyava koMDAcamanava mADi |
ivu jIrNavappaMte svarNadajAMDavane Basmava mADi matte sEvisida || 23 ||
kudiva bAhyOdakaveMba kaShAyava mudadiMda koMDu tEgutali |
padumeyoDane innu pavaDisabEkeMdu budhavaMdyanaMdu bayasida || 24 ||
oMdoMdu nimiShayaMdaduMDu tEgi eMdinaMtippa mukuMdanetta |
oMdiShTannadhikavAdare noMdu talesuttidaMdugabaDuva jIvavRuMda[videtta] ||
25 ||
oMdoMdu guNake lekkavilleMba mahime baluceMdavAyitu iMdireyarasanalli |
hiMde iMdu muMdanaMtakAladi sRuShTipa oMdE guNa kriyAnaMtavallade || 26 ||
idE rIti rakShakatva shikShakatva mOkShapadadAtRutvAdi guNagaNavoMdoMdu |
padumanABana balAnaMtavAgade biDade aduButavallave namminiyanATa || 27 ||
oppuvaMgagaLoLu tOrpa surara hiMDu tappisi rameyeMtappuvaLo |
kappurada karaDigeyaMtippa bAyoLu tannappaniraleMtu cuMbipaLo || 29 ||

adariMda tanna maiyoLagidda jIvara udaradi bacciDalu |
udadhikannike tanna ratiganuvAge nEhada bagege manadoLubbidaLu || 30 ||
terateradi miMcuva tamma dEhaMgaLa siri pasarise siridharana |
puramUraroLagirda pUrvamuktaru baMdu hariyudarava pokkarAga || 31 ||
ella jIvara tanna poTTeyoLiTTu siriyollaBa nidregoLisida |
sallIleyiMdali satiyoDanADuva ullAsagaLa kANadaMte || 32 ||
iMtu muktAmukta jIvara tiMtiNiyanAMtu shrIkAMta pavaDisi |
kAMteyaroDane saMtOShadaliha kathe saMtata namma salahali || 33 ||
shlOka - shrIrEva lOkarUpENa viShNOstiShThati sarvadA |
atO hi vaiShNavA lOkA nityAstEcEtanA api ||
shrIdEvi tAne tridhAma nAmakiyAgi Adi^^aMtyagaLilladaMte |
bOdha suKarUpaLAgihaLeMdu pUrvadA vEdavAdigaLOdutiharu || 34 ||
adariMda hariya mUlOkaMgaLige layada kicciMda kEDilla |
modalOdakagaLella pOdakAraNa lakumi udadhiyAdaLacyutage || 35 ||
shlOka - salilaM shrI prakRutyAKyaM tadAsItkila kEvalaM
aMBastha cEtanAnyEti shrutyarthamudadarshayat |
yathaikAtmyAnuBAvEna vikalparahitaH svayaM
BUShaNAyudha liMgAdyA dhattE shaktIH svamayayaM ||
tatvagaLigatidUravAda dEshadali jagattina praLayakAladali |
Bartage rame tAne BUShaNAyudha aMga vastramAlegaLAgihaLu gaDa || 36 ||
aMbudhiyAdaLe Aga mahalakumi aMbarABaraNavAgihaLu |
poMbaNNadAladeleyu tAnAdaLEneMbenavaLa sAhasavanu || 37 ||
maMdAra kusumada mAle tAnAdaLu gaMdhaparimaLavAgihaLu |
maMdamArutavAgi suttalU suLivaLu iMdireyiravanEneMbe || 38 ||

muKa nODe caMdramana sobaga[mIridaLAgi] suKa vacanadi shukOktigaLa |
pikanaMte pADuvaLu prANanAyakanige sakalasaMBrama tOridaLu || 39 ||
tuMbi suLivaMte kaMgaLanOTadiMdaMbujAkShanigartiyittu |
biMbAdharadoLippa sudheya rasavavanige cuMbisiyuNisidaLA bAle || 40 ||
shlOka - asAvEkArNavI BUtE mAyAvaTadaLE pumAn |
jagatsvajaTharE biBrattasmin shEtE janArdanaH ||
BU lakShmI durgE[ru]lAlisutire hari AladeleyamEle malagi |
A layAMbudhiya kallOla udakadalluyyAleyADidanAga lIleyali || 41 ||
omme BUmiyahaLomme durgiyahaLomme shrIdEviyAgihaLu |
immaiyalomme patiyappalu suKipa cinmayaLartiyanEneMbe || 42 ||
ivaLappikoMbAga hariya vakShada gaMdha avaLuradalli tOrutihudu |
avaLa cuMbisidAga patiya daMtada gAya ivaLadharadalopputihudu || 43 ||
accutanudaradi liMgadEhada kaNNamucci jIvaru nidregaiye |
eccattihanu gaDa muKyaprANanu obba svacCacitta muktaroLage || 44 ||
praLayEpi avilupta bAhyajnaveMdaKiLaroLu muKya mArutana |
neleyaritu vAyurvAva nitya eMba nirmaLa shruti garjisuttidako || 45 ||
dEhi nidritanAge avana dEhadoLiha jIvaru nidreya baDaru |
hOha bAha shvAsaMgaLAga naDesuvanIhada layada kAladali || 46 ||
shlOka - layasyahyaShTamEBAgE sRuShTikAla udAhRutaH |
tatraiva vEdasaMcArO yOnyathA viShNubuddhigA ||
bommanna nUruvaruSha praLayadamAna tanmadhye eMBattELvare abda |
summane hOhudu adara tudiyalli namma durgammageccarike || 47 ||

shlOka - svasRuShTamida mApIya shayAnaM saha shaktiBiH
tadaMtE BOdhayAMcakruH talliMgaiH shrutayaH paraM |
jayajaya jahyajAmajita dOShagRuhItaguNAM
tvamasi yadAtmanA samavaruddha samasta BagaH ||
aja jagadOka sAmaKila shaktyAvabOdhaka tE
kvacidajayAtmanAnucaratOnucarEnnigamaH |
svaguNAcCAdikAM hatvA paramAcCAdikAM paraH
vyAGaTya mOkShapadavIM dadAti puruShOttamaH ||
eMdeMdu nAshavillada prakRuti tA ninnaMdava kANalIyaLo |
iMdvarkakOTigaLa geluva ninna tEjOvRuMdakke innobbaridire || 48 ||
ivaLa kollabEDa jIvAvarkaMgaLa vivaradiMdavaLa tolagisu |
avaLalladinnu jIvara kaNge ninna muccuvar^yAro mU[ja]gadoLage || 49 ||
hInajIvara tuccajnAnAdi guNagaLa nAnyAke baMdhisabEku |
I nIcakarmakke nija aMsha sAkeMdu tAne jagadrUpaLAgihaLu || 50 ||
niravadhika mahime ninnAjneyiMdali ariyadaMtAcarisuvaLu |
hari ninna mAyeyakollabEDa jIvarAvarka mAyeya kollu kollu || 51 ||
jIvAvarkaMgaLoLageraDu mAyegaLihavu dEva nI mAya dUranallE |
shrI vidhipUrvaka shaktiprErakaneMdu BAme gaMDana koMDADidaLu || 52 ||
pAdavanottutta sakalavEdaMgaLa hAdigaLAlOcanadi |
Odutta pADutta pogaLutiralu kELi mOdi hayavadana kaNtereda || 53 ||
iMtu lakShmiyoDane praLayadi malagi shrIkAMtaneccattaneMballi |
saMtOShavanIva eraDane saMdhi saMtaru mecce mugiyitu || 54 ||
shrIdhara hayavadanarAyana dayadiMda vAdirAjEMdra racisida |
I divyakAvyadi layavanoreva ramyada dvitIya saMdhi posabage || 55 ||
|| BAratIramaNa muKyaprANAMtargata shrIkRuShNArpaNamastu ||
